featured_question.question: Could some one please help me with the friday prayer timing at ds mosque? We r coming on 22oct
featured_question.answer:
Time table for Friday Prayer khutba is about 12:45 pm following which  prayer starts at 13 :00 hrs at Choti Musjid, Darjeeling.
And exactly at 13:00 hrs khutba starts at Bari Musjid following which prayer starts simultaneously.
